    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 that defines mechanical purity. This specimen features the high-revving S54 inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for razor-sharp throttle response. The powertrain is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock for superior corner-exit traction. Significant preventative maintenance has been completed, including rod bearing replacement and comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension remains tight with refreshed bushings and dampers, maintaining the original factory-tuned kinematics. This is an uncompromising example of BMW's engineering peak, presented in showroom condition with a documented service history.",
